OL,5, A woman who said her last wish was to  
OL,6, meet Tom Hardy was rewarded with a     
OL,7, video call from her hero after a social
OL,8, media appeal.                          
OL,10,FSuperfan Jo-Anne Shaw, who is receiving
OL,11,Fend-of-life care at Myton Hospice in   
OL,12,FWarwick, told staff that was the one   
OL,13,Fthing she dreamed of.                  
OL,15,FThey put an appeal on social media and 
OL,16,Fthe actor responded on Instagram       
OL,17,Fsaying: "Be my pleasure."              
OL,19,FHe video-called her on Friday and Mrs  
OL,20,FShaw said: "He has made my day."       
